---
import MainLayout from '@/layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Студия покоя — MindHub24"
  description="Звуки природы, медитации, частоты гармонии. Всё работает прямо в браузере. Бесплатно. Анонимно."
>

<style>
  body, .page-wrapper, main {
    background: #0B1520;
  }
</style>

<!-- Audio Init Overlay -->
<div id="audioInitOverlay" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center px-4" style="background: rgba(11,21,32,0.95);">
  <div class="text-center max-w-sm">
    <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6" style="background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);">
      <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round">
        <path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-white mb-3">Студия покоя</h2>
    <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mb-8">Нажмите, чтобы активировать аудио. Все звуки генерируются прямо в браузере — ничего не скачивается.</p>
    <button id="audioInitBtn" class="px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-base font-medium transition-all hover:opacity-90" style="background: var(--color-accent); color: var(--color-deep);">
      Начать
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Page Header -->
<div class="text-center py-12 px-4" style="background: #0B1520; color: white;">
  <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-2" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Бесплатно · Анонимно · Без регистрации</p>
  <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white mb-3">Студия покоя</h1>
  <p class="text-white/50 text-base max-w-md mx-auto">Звуки природы, медитации, частоты гармонии. Всё работает в вашем браузере.</p>
</div>

<!-- Tab Nav -->
<div class="sticky top-16 z-30 flex border-b" style="background: #0F1C28; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
  <button class="studio-tab flex-1 py-4 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-white/50 hover:text-white border-b-2 border-transparent" data-tab="sounds">Звуки</button>
  <button class="studio-tab flex-1 py-4 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-white/50 hover:text-white border-b-2 border-transparent" data-tab="frequencies">Частоты</button>
  <button class="studio-tab flex-1 py-4 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-white/50 hover:text-white border-b-2 border-transparent" data-tab="meditations">Медитации</button>
  <button class="studio-tab flex-1 py-4 text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200 text-white/50 hover:text-white border-b-2 border-transparent" data-tab="breathe">Дыхание</button>
</div>

<!-- TAB 1: AMBIENT SOUND MIXER -->
<div id="tab-sounds" class="studio-panel px-4 py-10" style="background: #0B1520; min-height: 80vh;">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-white mb-2 text-center">Смешайте свои звуки</h2>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm text-center mb-8">Выберите один или несколько. Настройте громкость.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10" id="soundGrid"></div>

    <!-- Master volume -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <label class="text-xs text-white/40 mb-2 block">Общая громкость</label>
      <input type="range" id="masterVolume" min="0" max="100" value="70" class="w-full accent-[#C9A84C]" />
    </div>

    <!-- Timer -->
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-3">
      <button class="timer-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30" data-minutes="5">5 мин</button>
      <button class="timer-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30" data-minutes="15">15 мин</button>
      <button class="timer-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30" data-minutes="30">30 мин</button>
      <button class="timer-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30 active-timer" data-minutes="0">∞</button>
    </div>
    <p id="timerDisplay" class="text-center text-white/30 text-xs mt-3"></p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TAB 2: SOLFEGGIO FREQUENCIES -->
<div id="tab-frequencies" class="studio-panel px-4 py-10" style="background: #0B1520; display: none; min-height: 80vh;">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-white mb-2 text-center">Частоты гармонии</h2>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm text-center mb-6">Выберите частоту по вашему состоянию</p>

    <!-- Quick presets -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center mb-8">
      <button class="preset-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs text-white/60 border border-white/15 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-preset="sleep">Перед сном</button>
      <button class="preset-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs text-white/60 border border-white/15 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-preset="anxiety">Снять тревогу</button>
      <button class="preset-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs text-white/60 border border-white/15 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-preset="meditation">Медитация</button>
      <button class="preset-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs text-white/60 border border-white/15 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-preset="focus">Концентрация</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Frequency cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-8" id="freqGrid"></div>

    <p class="text-center text-white/25 text-xs">Для лучшего эффекта используйте наушники</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TAB 3: GUIDED MEDITATIONS -->
<div id="tab-meditations" class="studio-panel px-4 py-10" style="background: #0B1520; display: none; min-height: 80vh;">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-white mb-2 text-center">Направленные медитации</h2>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm text-center mb-8">Аудио-сопровождение генерируется автоматически. Наушники рекомендуются.</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4" id="meditationList"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Fullscreen meditation player -->
<div id="meditationPlayer" class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4" style="background: #0B1520; display: none;">
  <button id="closeMeditation" class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-white/40 hover:text-white text-sm flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors">
    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
    Завершить
  </button>

  <div class="max-w-md w-full text-center">
    <div id="meditationTextBlock" class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 leading-relaxed mb-8 min-h-[160px] flex items-center justify-center" style="white-space: pre-line;"></div>
    <div class="text-white/25 text-xs mb-6" id="meditationProgress"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Progress bar -->
  <div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
    <div id="meditationProgressBar" class="h-full transition-all duration-500" style="background: var(--color-accent); width: 0%;"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TAB 4: BREATHING -->
<div id="tab-breathe" class="studio-panel px-4 py-10 text-center" style="background: #0B1520; display: none; min-height: 80vh;">
  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-white mb-8">Дыхательная практика</h2>

    <!-- Pattern selector -->
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mb-10">
      <button class="breathe-pattern-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs border border-white/20 text-white/60 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-pattern="relax">Расслабление 4-4-6</button>
      <button class="breathe-pattern-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs border border-white/20 text-white/60 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-pattern="balance">Баланс 4-4-4</button>
      <button class="breathe-pattern-btn px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-xs border border-white/20 text-white/60 hover:border-white/40 transition-colors" data-pattern="calm">Успокоение 4-7-8</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Breathing circle -->
    <div class="relative mx-auto mb-8 flex items-center justify-center" style="width: 200px; height: 200px;">
      <div id="breatheCircle" class="rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all" style="width: 120px; height: 120px; border-color: var(--color-accent); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.2);">
        <p id="breatheText" class="text-white font-heading text-lg">—</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p id="breatheCycleInfo" class="text-white/30 text-xs mb-6">Нажмите «Начать», чтобы начать</p>

    <!-- Duration pills -->
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-3 mb-8">
      <button class="breathe-duration px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors" data-minutes="3">3 мин</button>
      <button class="breathe-duration px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors" data-minutes="5">5 мин</button>
      <button class="breathe-duration px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-white/50 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30 transition-colors" data-minutes="10">10 мин</button>
    </div>

    <button id="breatheStart" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-base font-medium transition-all hover:opacity-90" style="background: var(--color-accent); color: var(--color-deep);">Начать</button>
    <button id="breatheStop" class="hidden px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-base font-medium transition-all" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white;">Остановить</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Bottom CTA -->
<section class="py-16 px-4 text-center" style="background: #0B1520;">
  <p class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/80 italic mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto">
    «Практики помогают. Но иногда нужен человек, который просто будет рядом.»
  </p>
  <a href="/book" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:opacity-90" style="background: var(--color-accent); color: var(--color-deep);">
    Записаться на бесплатный 15-минутный звонок
  </a>
  <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/30">Онлайн · Бесплатно · Конфиденциально</p>
  <p class="mt-8 text-xs text-white/20 max-w-sm mx-auto">Студия покоя — это инструмент релаксации, а не медицинское лечение. При серьёзных трудностях обратитесь к специалисту.</p>
</section>

</MainLayout>

